      h3 Tabs
      p Takes the basic nav from above and adds the <code>.nav-tabs</code> class to generate a tabbed interface. Use them to create tabbable regions with our tab JavaScript plugin.

      .bd-example
        ul.nav.nav-tabs
          li.nav-item
            a.nav-link.active(aria-current='page' href='#') Active
          li.nav-item
            a.nav-link(href='#') Link
          li.nav-item
            a.nav-link(href='#') Link
          li.nav-item
            a.nav-link.disabled(aria-disabled='true') Disabled

