      h3 Working with flex utilities
      p If you need responsive nav variations, consider using a series of flexbox utilities. While more verbose, these utilities offer greater customization across responsive breakpoints. In the example below, our nav will be stacked on the lowest breakpoint, then adapt to a horizontal layout that fills the available width starting from the small breakpoint.

      .bd-example
        nav.nav.nav-pills.flex-column.flex-sm-row
          a.flex-sm-fill.text-sm-center.nav-link.active(aria-current='page' href='#') Active
          a.flex-sm-fill.text-sm-center.nav-link(href='#') Longer nav link
          a.flex-sm-fill.text-sm-center.nav-link(href='#') Link
          a.flex-sm-fill.text-sm-center.nav-link.disabled(aria-disabled='true') Disabled

      pre
