          |   &lt;a class="flex-sm-fill text-sm-center nav-link disabled" aria-disabled="true"&gt;Disabled&lt;/a&gt;
          | &lt;/nav&gt;

      h3 Using dropdowns
      p Add dropdown menus with a little extra HTML and the dropdowns JavaScript plugin.

